node.text:
Happy Happy Hour! The best accessory is a smile - and it's best paired with the voice behind it. On today's Happy Hour At Home, Katie Grossbard of @iamavoter walks us through the four ways you can vote this year, and answers some common FAQs about mail-in ballots. 

Remember, our democracy works best when we all participate - so make your voting plan now! And don't forget - 10% of the proceeds of our I Vote Necklace (that Katie is wearing here!) go to @iamavoter.

node.title: Happy Hour At Home with I am a voter.®

node.text: Happy Happy Hour! Today Founder & CEO of @wearlively, @the_michellegrant, is showing us her quarantine-inspired "Daily Elixir" - an energizing & healthy option you can make right in the comfort of your very own kitchen. On August 17th, Michelle will be launching a series called "Office Hours" on her personal IG where she'll be offering tangible advice for up and coming business owners and entrepreneurs!  Applicants can sign up on the form that will be available in the link in her bio starting on the 17th, and the first LIVE office hours will be August 25th - so make sure to tune in!

node.text: Happy Happy Hour! node.text: Happy Happy Hour! Calling all dessert lovers - this week we're featuring @oddfellowsnyc , BB's personal favorite ice cream shop ☺️They're showing you how to make a banana split at home, and sharing with you the best wine pairings for your sweet summer treat (which you can get with your order at their locations - they're the only ice cream shop in the country that does so!). OddFellows is currently open in NYC at their DUMBO location Fridays-Sundays, and at their Chestnut Hill location Thursday-Sundays, with full hours coming soon! National shipping is also coming to their website in June, oddfellowsnyc.com, and local delivery is available in NYC and Boston. Head on over, and kick off the new season in a delicious way! 🍦

node.text: Happy Happy Hour! This week, recipe developer and author Caroline Chambers (@carochambers) is showing us an easy & delicious cocktail recipe to start your weekend off right! 🎉 Caroline's cookbook, Just Married, is the perfect go-to for couples and recipes for two, and is available for purchase via Amazon and Crate & Barrel. More simple, no-stress recipes with big flavor are on Caroline's page and website, carolinechambers.com - head on over for some tasty ideas! ☺️

It's All You: Introducing not one, but TWO new custom bracelets to our best-selling Pisa collection. As an evolution to the classic gold ball bead, our newest bead design creates a chic, pleated effect on your wrist for effortless stacking. Which style will you choose to add? ⬇️

Custom Pavé Tile Pisa Bracelet:  Revamp your wrist stack with something handmade just for you. Innovative, gold beads create a pleated effect on the band that's extra sleek. Topped off with pavé beads, it's a must-have in your accessory arsenal. Pick a name or phrase for extra fun personalization.

Custom Rainbow Tile Pisa Bracelet: We added gold pleated beads to ensure a super comfortable band, translucent letter beads for just a subtle hint of color, and extra detailed gold-plated letters to make your personalization pop. Our letter beads now come in a tile shape that modernizes the classic friendship bracelet.

(Pssst...can't decide? Take 20% off 2+ bracelets with code STACKING20)
